<li>Find the trapezoid <strong>height</strong>;</li>
<li>Calculate the trapezoid <strong>perimeter</strong>; and</li>
<li>Calculate the trapezoid <strong><a href=3D"https://www.calctool.org/con=
version/angle-converter" class=3D"js-link">angles</a></strong>.</li>
</ul>
<p>Read on if you want to learn how to find the trapezoid height, area, or =
